<Script 1> 
  name: 
    bed_region_ann.pl
  
  description:
    This is a simple Perl script to find the genes in defined regions
  
  usage:
    perl bed_region_ann.pl [option] --gff <in.gff> --bed <in.bed> --out <out>
  
  option:
   --col    three cols to define one region [1,2,3]
   --extend extend length around defined BED region [0]
   --help   help information
  
  note:
    GFF file is 1-based and however BED file is 0-based in this script
  
  example: 
    bed_region_ann.pl --gff ../../../00.genome/moso.hic_merge.gff --bed cnv.bed --out cnv.ann.bed
